#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn6.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn6.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The Appeal "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 7. Kokālikasutta → kokālikasuttaṃ (1) (s1, pts2) | paṭhamakokālikasuttaṃ (s2, s3)
msgctxt "sn6.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Kokālikasutta "
msgstr "7. About Kokālika "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn6.7:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.7:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā divāvihāragato hoti paṭisallīno. "
msgstr "Now at that time the Buddha had gone into retreat for the day’s meditation. "

msgctxt "sn6.7:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho subrahmā ca paccekabrahmā suddhāvāso ca paccekabrahmā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā paccekaṃ dvārabāhaṃ nissāya aṭṭhaṃsu. "
msgstr "Then the independent brahmās Subrahmā and Suddhāvāsa went to the Buddha and stationed themselves one by each door-post. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.7:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho subrahmā paccekabrahmā kokālikaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Subrahmā recited this verse about the mendicant Kokālika in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.323, sc2
msgctxt "sn6.7:2.1"
msgid "“Appameyyaṃ paminanto, "
msgstr "“What wise person here would judge "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.7:2.2"
msgid "Kodha vidvā vikappaye; "
msgstr "the immeasurable by measuring them? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.7:2.3"
msgid "Appameyyaṃ pamāyinaṃ, "
msgstr "I think anyone who’d do such a thing "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.7:2.4"
msgid "Nivutaṃ taṃ maññe puthujjanan”ti. "
msgstr "must be an ordinary person, wrapped in darkness.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
